column2: SELECT m.id as [id], str (m.ra, #, #) AS ra, str (m.dec, #, #) AS dec, str (sp.modelMag_u, #, #) as u, str (sp.modelMagErr_u, #, #) as err_u, str (sp.modelMag_g, #, #) as g, str (sp.modelMagErr_g, #, #) as err_g, str (sp.modelMag_i, #, #) as r, str (sp.modelMagErr_i, #, #) as err_i, str (sp.modelMag_r, #, #) as r, str (sp.modelMagErr_r, #, #) as err_r, sp.plate, sp.fiberid, sp.mjd, sp.z, sp.zwarning, pz.z, sp.class into mydb.listMgIIphot_t3 from MyDB.listMgIIphot AS m OUTER APPLY dbo.fGetNearestObjEq (m.ra, m.dec, #) AS n LEFT OUTER JOIN SpecPhotoAll AS sp ON n.objID = sp.objID LEFT OUTER JOIN SpecObjAll AS s ON s.specobjID = sp.specobjID LEFT OUTER JOIN Photoz AS pz ON pz.objID = sp.objID WHERE (sp.z > = #) OR (pz.z > = #)
